              "desc": "被血染黑，變得如鋼鐵一般堅硬的乾花。對故主而言，是某種紀念品吧。",
              "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Bloodstained Chivalry/flower_of_life_icon.png",
